Even if you dont like Chaplin, or R.Downey.Jr.,this is a must see for
every
one. The acting is phenomenal. Robert was robbed
of the Oscar for this one. I never knew much about Chaplin, or liked him
that well, but you have to put yourself in that day, technology, the
performing arts and humor.Chaplin lived a very challenging life, and took
it
all with a &quot;SMILE&quot;
